        <h1 class="section-title osrs-gold-text">Help Center</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400">Welcome to the OSRS DMM Tracker Help Center. Find answers to common questions and learn how to maximize your gold-making potential in Deadman Mode.</p>
        
