            <summary class="text-lg font-semibold osrs-gold-text">How do I use the Profit Leaderboard?</summary>
            <div class="text-gray-400 space-y-2">
              <p>The Profit Leaderboard shows the top 20 items with the highest profit margins in DMM. Here's how to use it:</p>
              <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-1">
