                <li>Look at the "Sell Price (High)" column - this is the price to place your sell offer</li>
                <li>The "Margin" column shows your potential profit per item</li>
                <li>Click "Refresh" to get the latest prices</li>
              </ol>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="osrs-card p-6">
            <summary class="text-lg font-semibold osrs-gold-text">What do the swap rates mean?</summary>
            <div class="text-gray-400 space-y-2">
              <p>The swap rate (e.g., "1M DMM = 55M OSRS") shows the current exchange rate between Deadman Mode gold and regular OSRS gold.</p>
              <p>This is useful if you want to understand the real-world value of your DMM earnings or if you're considering swapping gold between game modes.</p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="osrs-card p-6">
            <summary class="text-lg font-semibold osrs-gold-text">How do I flip items for profit?</summary>
            <div class="text-gray-400 space-y-2">
              <p>Flipping is the process of buying items low and selling them high. Here's a basic guide:</p>
              <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-1">
                <li>Find an item with a good margin on our leaderboard (higher = better)</li>
                <li>Go to the Grand Exchange in-game</li>
                <li>Place a buy offer at or slightly above the "Low" price</li>
                <li>Once bought, place a sell offer at or slightly below the "High" price</li>
                <li>Wait for your offer to complete - the difference is your profit!</li>
              </ol>
              <p class="mt-3"><strong class="text-amber-400">Tip:</strong> Start with items that have high trading volume for faster sales.</p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="osrs-card p-6">
            <summary class="text-lg font-semibold osrs-gold-text">Why are some items filtered out?</summary>
            <div class="text-gray-400 space-y-2">
              <p>We automatically filter items to show only the most profitable opportunities:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
                <li><strong>Margin > 50,000 GP:</strong> Items with lower margins aren't worth the time</li>
                <li><strong>Traded in last hour:</strong> Ensures the prices are current and the item is actively traded</li>
              </ul>
              <p>This helps you focus on items that can actually make you money.</p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="osrs-card p-6">
            <summary class="text-lg font-semibold osrs-gold-text">How often is the data updated?</summary>
